    "sText_MysteryGiftAlteringCave": "Thank you for using the MYSTERY\\nGIFT System.\\pThere appears to be a rumor about\\nrare POKMON sightings.\\pThe sightings reportedly came from\\nthe ALTERING CAVE on ROUTE 103.\\pPerhaps it would be worthwhile for\\nyou to investigate this rumor.",
    "sText_AuroraTicketForYou": "Thank you for using the MYSTERY\\nGIFT System.\\pYou must be {PLAYER}.\\nThere is a ticket here for you.",
    "sText_AuroraTicketUseAtPort": "It appears to be for use at the\\nLILYCOVE CITY port.\\pWhy not give it a try and see what\\nit is about?",
    "sText_AuroraTicketThankYou": "Thank you for using the MYSTERY\\nGIFT System.",
    "sText_AuroraTicketBagFull": "Oh, I'm sorry, {PLAYER}.\\nYour BAG's KEY ITEMS POCKET is full.\\pPlease store something on your PC,\\nthen come back for this.",
    "sText_MysteryGiftBattleCountCard": "Thank you for using the MYSTERY\\nGIFT System.\\pYour BATTLE COUNT CARD keeps\\ntrack of your battle record against\\lTRAINERS with the same CARD.\\pLook for and battle TRAINERS who\\nhave the same CARD as you.\\pYou may check the overall rankings\\nby reading the NEWS.\\pPlease do give it a try!",
    "sText_MysteryGiftBattleCountCard_WonPrize": "Thank you for using the MYSTERY\\nGIFT System.\\pCongratulations!\\pYou have won a prize for winning\\nthree battles!\\pWe hope you will be inspired to\\nbattle some more.",
    "sText_MysticTicketForYou": "Thank you for using the MYSTERY\\nGIFT System.\\pYou must be {PLAYER}.\\nThere is a ticket here for you.",
    "sText_MysticTicketUseAtPort": "It appears to be for use at the\\nLILYCOVE CITY port.\\pWhy not give it a try and see what\\nit is about?",
    "sText_MysticTicketThankYou": "Thank you for using the MYSTERY\\nGIFT System.",
    "sText_MysticTicketBagFull": "Oh, I'm sorry, {PLAYER}.\\nYour BAG's KEY ITEMS POCKET is full.\\pPlease store something on your PC,\\nthen come back for this.",
    "sText_MysteryGiftOldSeaMapForYou": "Thank you for using the MYSTERY\\nGIFT System.\\pLet me confirm--you are {PLAYER}?\\pWe received this OLD SEA MAP\\naddressed to you.",
    "sText_MysteryGiftOldSeaMapUseAtPort": "It appears to be for use at the\\nLILYCOVE CITY port.\\pWhy not give it a try and see what\\nit is about?",
    "sText_MysteryGiftOldSeaMapThankYou": "Thank you for using the MYSTERY\\nGIFT System.",
    "sText_MysteryGiftOldSeaMapBagFull": "Oh, I'm sorry, {PLAYER}.\\nYour BAG's KEY ITEMS POCKET is full.\\pPlease store something on your PC,\\nthen come back for this.",
    "sText_MysteryGiftEgg": "Thank you for using the MYSTERY\\nGIFT System.\\pFrom the POKMON CENTER we\\nhave a gift--a POKMON EGG!\\pPlease raise it with love and\\nkindness.",
    "sText_FullParty": "Oh, your party appears to be full.\\pPlease come see me after storing\\na POKMON on a PC.",
    "sText_MysteryGiftStampCard": "Thank you for using the STAMP CARD\\nSystem.\\pYou have {STR_VAR_1} more to collect to\\nfill your STAMP CARD.",
    "sText_MysteryGiftVisitingTrainerInstructions": "Thank you for using the MYSTERY\\nGIFT System.\\pBy holding this WONDER CARD, you\\nmay take part in a survey at a\\lPOKMON MART.\\pUse these surveys to invite\\nTRAINERS to SOOTOPOLIS CITY.\\pLet me give you a secret\\npassword for a survey:\\pGIVE ME\\nAWESOME TRAINER\\pWrite that in on a survey and send\\nit to the WIRELESS\\lCOMMUNICATION SYSTEM.",
    "sText_MysteryGiftVisitingTrainerArrived": "Thank you for using the MYSTERY\\nGIFT System.\\pA TRAINER has arrived in\\nSOOTOPOLIS CITY looking for you.\\pWe hope you will enjoy\\nbattling the visiting TRAINER.\\pYou may invite other TRAINERS by\\nentering other passwords.\\pTry looking for other passwords\\nthat may work.",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_ImTheFavorLady": "I'm the FAVOR LADY",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_ObsessedWithThing": "I've recently developed an obsession\\nfor {STR_VAR_1} things",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_ThankYouForLastTime": "Oh\\nThank you for last time",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_PlayerGaveMeBadThing": "Before, I think it was {STR_VAR_3}\\p{STR_VAR_3} gave me one {STR_VAR_2},\\nsaying it was {STR_VAR_1}.\\pBut it wasn't {STR_VAR_1}.\\nNot in the least bit.",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_PlayerGaveMeGreatThing": "Before, {STR_VAR_3} gave me a very\\n{STR_VAR_1} {STR_VAR_2}.\\pI cherish it now.",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_WillYouShareThing": "Listen, if you have anything that\\nis {STR_VAR_1}, will you share it\\lwith me?",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_WhatWillYouGiveMe": "Really?\\nWhat will you give me?",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_IsThatSoGoodbye": "Is that so?\\nThen, it's good-bye",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_NotWillingToShare": "Oh\\nYou're not willing to share?",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_IllTryToCherishIt": "Oh?\\nThat {STR_VAR_2} is {STR_VAR_1}?\\pOh, is that right?\\pWell, I owe you a thanks anyway.\\nI'll try to cherish it",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_IWillCherishThis": "Oh\\pThat's a quite {STR_VAR_1}\\n{STR_VAR_2}\\pIsn't it nice?\\nIt's so dreamy\\pThank you\\nI will cherish this",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_IWillTreasureThis": "Oh, oh, oh\\pThis is amazing!\\nThis really is {STR_VAR_1}!\\pI never knew that one {STR_VAR_2}\\ncould be this {STR_VAR_1}!\\pThank you!\\pI will treasure this for the rest\\nof my life!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_IllGiveYouThisInReturn": "I'll give you this wonderful item in\\nreturn for your fabulous gift.\\pI hope you will cherish it",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_YouDontHaveSpaceForIt": "Oh, you can't have it if you don't have\\nthe space for it.\\pPlease come see me when you get\\nyour BAG organized",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_ImTheQuizLady": "I'm the QUIZ LADY!\\nI love quizzes!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_WaitingToTakeYourQuiz": "Oh?\\pI'm waiting for a challenger to answer\\nthe quiz you made.\\pWe can chat another time, okay?",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_WaitingForChallenger": "I'm waiting for someone to challenge\\na quiz this {STR_VAR_1} thought up!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_TakeQuizChallenge": "If you answer correctly, you can win\\nfabulous prizes!\\pWould you like to take the quiz\\nchallenge?",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_WaitForAnswer": "     \\n     ",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_HowBoringBye": "Oh, how boring!\\nBye-bye!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_YoureGoingToQuit": "Awww!\\nYou're going to quit?",
