    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_YouGotItRight": "You're amazing! You've got it right!\\nYou're one sharp customer!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_YouGotItRightYouveWonPersonsPrize": "Congratulations!\\nYou've got the quiz right!\\pYou've won a prize provided by\\n{STR_VAR_1}!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_XReceivedOneY": "{STR_VAR_1} received\\none {STR_VAR_2}!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_YourBagIsFilledUp": "Oh? Your BAG is filled up!\\nCome see me when you have room.",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_WrongTheCorrectAnswerIs": "Hmm Wrong!\\nThe correct answer is {STR_VAR_3}!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_IGetToKeepPrize": "Too bad!\\pI get to keep the quiz prize\\n{STR_VAR_1} now!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_MakeYourOwnQuiz": "Listen, listen!\\nWould you like to make your own quiz?",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_MaybeNextTime": "Oh, I see\\nWell, maybe next time!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_PickYourPrize": "Okay, the first thing you have to do\\nis pick the prize for the person that\\lanswers your quiz correctly.\\pBut beware, if the person taking\\nthe quiz can't get it right, I get to\\lkeep the prize!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_QuitChoosingPrize": "If you don't choose a prize,\\nyour quiz can't be made.\\pAre you going to quit making\\nyour quiz?",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_WriteYourQuiz": "Oh, how nice!\\nThat's a wonderful prize!\\pNext, you need to write your quiz\\nquestion and its answer.",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_QuitWritingQuizQuestion": "Are you going to quit writing\\nyour quiz question?",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_QuitWritingQuizAnswer": "Are you going to quit choosing\\nyour quiz answer?",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_IllLookForAChallenger": "Thank you!\\nYou've put together a nice quiz.\\pI'll go look for someone who'll take\\nyour quiz challenge right away.",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_ImTheContestLady": "I'm the CONTEST LADY!\\nI sure do love CONTESTS!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_ThankForPokeblock": "Thanks for your {POKEBLOCK} before!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_MyFriendDisplaysQuality": "This is my friend {STR_VAR_1}!\\nIt's the epitome of {STR_VAR_2}!\\pBut I think that it will display\\neven more {STR_VAR_2}!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_DontHaveAPokeblockCase": "So, I need your help!\\pPlease, may I have one {POKEBLOCK}?\\nAll I'm asking for is one!\\pOh, but\\nDon't you have a {POKEBLOCK} CASE?\\lThat's no good. Next time, then!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_AskingForOnePokeblock": "So, I need your help!\\pPlease, may I have one {POKEBLOCK}?\\nAll I'm asking for is one!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_ICantHaveOnePokeblock": "Awww!\\nI can't have one {POKEBLOCK}?!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_WhatACheapskate": "Sheesh!\\nWhat a cheapskate!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_IllUseYourPokeblock": "Yay!\\nThank you!\\pI'll feed my POKMON your {POKEBLOCK}\\nright away.",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_NoChangeThanks": "It doesn't seem to have changed\\nin any way at all\\pHmm\\pOh, well!\\nThank you very much!",
    "LilycoveCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_ReallyImprovedThanks": "Oh, yay!\\nIt's really delighted!\\pI think it really improved {STR_VAR_1}'s\\n{STR_VAR_2} quality, too.\\pThank you so much!",
