    "MauvilleCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_CantTradeThatOne": "Oops! Sorry! That's a really rare\\npiece of decoration.\\lI can't trade that one away!\\pCan I interest you in something else?",
    "MauvilleCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_WillYouHearMyTale": "I'm the STORYTELLER.\\nI'll tell you tales of legendary\\lTRAINERS.\\pWill you hear my tale?",
    "MauvilleCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_StorytellerFeelingTheBlues": "Oh\\nYou've left me feeling the blues",
