    "MauvilleCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_IKnowNoTales": "But, I know of no legendary TRAINERS.\\nHence, I know no tales.\\pWhere does one find a TRAINER worthy\\nof a legendary tale?",
    "MauvilleCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_YouDidStatXTimes": "What's that?!\\nYou You\\p{STR_VAR_2}\\n{STR_VAR_1} time(s)?!\\pThat is indeed magnificent!\\nIt's the birth of a new legend!",
    "MauvilleCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_CouldThereBeOtherLegends": "It gets me thinking, could there be\\nother TRAINERS with more impressive\\llegends awaiting discovery?",
    "MauvilleCity_PokemonCenter_1F_Text_HaveYouAnyLegendaryTales": "Are you a TRAINER?\\pThen tell me, have you any tales that\\nare even remotely legendary?",
