    "ProfileMan_Text_CollectTrainerProfiles": "Hello there, TRAINER!\\nYou've got a wonderful smile, there.\\pI have a hobby--collecting the profiles\\nof POKMON TRAINERS.",
    "ProfileMan_Text_MayISeeYourProfile": "So, how about it?\\nMay I see your profile?",
    "ProfileMan_Text_EasyChatExplanation": "You make your own profile by putting\\ntogether four words or phrases.\\pHere, I'll show you an example of a\\nprofile using four pieces of text.\\pYou can switch those four pieces with\\nother text pieces any which way you\\llike to make your own profile.\\pThere are a lot of text pieces that\\nyou can use.\\pThey are arranged in groups like\\nPOKMON, lifestyles, and hobbies so\\lit is easier to look them up.\\pSo, first, choose the group of text\\npieces to display a list of choices.\\pThen, pick the choice you want.\\pRepeat for the remaining text choices,\\nand you'll have your very own profile.",
    "ProfileMan_Text_LetsSeeItThen": "Yes! Thank you!\\nSo, let's see it, then.",
