    "SafariZone_Text_PokeblockStillHere": "The {STR_VAR_1} you left\\nbefore is still here.",
    "SafariZone_Text_PokeblockWasPlaced": "The {STR_VAR_1} was placed\\non the {POKEBLOCK} FEEDER.",
    "Route121_SafariZoneEntrance_Text_WelcomeToSafariZone": "Welcome to the SAFARI ZONE!\\pHere, you may witness many kinds of\\nPOKMON rarely seen in HOENN.\\pAnd, you'll see them in their wild,\\nuntamed state in natural habitats.\\pWhat's more, we've thrown open the\\ngates to POKMON TRAINERS.\\pYou're encouraged to catch POKMON\\nfor keeps!\\pCome in and enjoy the SAFARI ZONE!",
    "Route121_SafariZoneEntrance_Text_WelcomeFirstTime": "Welcome to the SAFARI ZONE!\\nIs it your first time here?",
    "Route121_SafariZoneEntrance_Text_ComeInAndEnjoy": "Come in and enjoy the SAFARI ZONE!",
    "Route121_SafariZoneEntrance_Text_FirstTimeInfo": "When you enter the SAFARI ZONE, you\\nstart with 30 SAFARI BALLS for\\lcatching POKMON.\\pThe SAFARI Game is over when you run\\nout of SAFARI BALLS, or when you've\\lwalked 500 steps.\\pCome in and enjoy the SAFARI ZONE!",
    "Route121_SafariZoneEntrance_Text_WouldYouLikeToPlay": "Welcome to the SAFARI ZONE!\\pAll you can catch for just 500!\\nWould you like to play a SAFARI Game?",
    "Route121_SafariZoneEntrance_Text_PlayAnotherTime": "Okay.\\nPlease play another time!",
    "Route121_SafariZoneEntrance_Text_NotEnoughMoney": "You don't have enough money.\\nSorry.",
    "Route121_SafariZoneEntrance_Text_ThatWillBe500Please": "That will be 500, please.",
    "Route121_SafariZoneEntrance_Text_HereAreYourSafariBalls": "Here are your SAFARI BALLS.",
    "Route121_SafariZoneEntrance_Text_Received30SafariBalls": "{PLAYER} received 30 SAFARI BALLS.",
    "Route121_SafariZoneEntrance_Text_PleaseEnjoyYourself": "We'll let you know when your game\\nis over.\\pSo, until then, enjoy yourself, please!\\nOff you go on your wild excursion!",
    "Route121_SafariZoneEntrance_Text_PCIsFull": "Excuse me!\\nYour PC BOX is full.",
    "Route121_SafariZoneEntrance_Text_YouNeedPokeblockCase": "Excuse me!\\nYou seem to be without a {POKEBLOCK} CASE.\\pYour SAFARI Game will be much more\\nfruitful if you use {POKEBLOCK}S.\\pPlease come back with a {POKEBLOCK} CASE.\\pYou may obtain a {POKEBLOCK} CASE from\\nthe LILYCOVE CONTEST HALL.",
    "SafariZone_South_Text_StillHaveTimeExit": "You still have time left. Would you like\\nto exit the SAFARI ZONE now?",
    "SafariZone_South_Text_EnjoyTheRestOfYourAdventure": "Please enjoy the rest of your wild\\nadventure!",
    "SafariZone_South_Text_ExitEarlyThankYouForPlaying": "Okay.\\pI'll take back your remaining SAFARI\\nBALLS.\\pThank you for playing.\\nWe hope to see you again.",
    "SafariZone_South_Text_GoodLuck": "Good luck!\\pIf you need anything, don't hesitate\\nto tell me, please!",
    "SafariZone_South_Text_Boy": "Did you know?\\pIf you put a {POKEBLOCK} in that square box,\\nPOKMON gather around.",
    "SafariZone_South_Text_Man": "I want to keep going deeper, but I\\nforgot to bring a BIKE.\\pSomething tells me that rare POKMON\\nlive in the outlying areas.",
    "SafariZone_Southwest_Text_Woman": "Sometimes, when I toss a {POKEBLOCK} at \\nPOKMON, it gets ignored.\\pDo POKMON have likes and dislikes\\nabout what they eat?",
    "SafariZone_Northwest_Text_Man": "Gasp Gasp\\nImade it out herebut\\pI'm exhausted I don't have the\\nenergy to catch POKMON",
    "SafariZone_North_Text_Fisherman": "I'm on a mission to find WATER POKMON\\nyou don't see in HOENN.\\pDo you have any idea where the lake is?",
    "SafariZone_North_Text_Man": "I'm going to catch a lot of rare POKMON\\nhere and trade them with my friends!",
    "SafariZone_South_Text_Youngster": "I put a {POKEBLOCK} on the {POKEBLOCK} FEEDER.\\nBut it seems to have disappeared.\\pI guess POKMON must have eaten it\\nwithout me noticing.",
    "Route121_SafariZoneEntrance_Text_TrainerTip": "SAFARI ZONE TRAINER TIP!\\pThrow {POKEBLOCK}S at wild POKMON to make\\nthem less likely to flee.",
    "SafariZone_Southwest_Text_RestHouseSign": "Relieve your tired feet.\\nREST HOUSE",
    "SafariZone_RestHouse_Text_Youngster": "I don't have any {POKEBLOCK}S, but I caught\\na good number of POKMON.\\pYou can improve your chances of making\\na catch by getting closer to them\\lbefore throwing a SAFARI BALL.",
    "SafariZone_RestHouse_Text_PsychicM": "If you use {POKEBLOCK}S, wild POKMON won't\\nbe so quick to run away.\\pIt's not much use to give {POKEBLOCK}S to\\nPOKMON that don't flee easily.",
    "SafariZone_RestHouse_Text_FatMan": "If you put a {POKEBLOCK} on the FEEDER,\\nPOKMON are attracted to it.\\pI think POKMON with the same sort of\\nnature are drawn by a certain {POKEBLOCK}.",
    "SafariZone_South_Text_AreaOffLimits1": "This area is still under construction.\\nIt's off-limits, sorry!",
    "SafariZone_Southeast_Text_ExpansionIsFinished": "The SAFARI ZONE's expansion project\\nis finished now.\\pWe hope you will enjoy the new area.",
